node.text: One more look back at 2019... what an amazing year. DADDY GANG!!! We can not say thank you enough for the support. We love you guys like ur our own giant group of friends. We started this show a little over a year ago and couldn’t be more thankful to everyone that has been a part of the ride with us. Meeting you in person, reading your stories, seeing you rock the merch, hearing the testimonials that all the moves we have brought to you like the god damn GLUCK GLUCK 9000 have helped your sex life, make us so proud to be doing this for you and with you guys. 2020 is going to be unreal for all of us. 2020 IS the year of the DADDY GANG!!! WE LOVE YOU! THE FATHERS ❤️❤️❤️❤️ @alexandracooper @sofiafranklyn
